lftp host.com
> ls
> cd contributed/ubuntu/8.04/             Change remote directory (with tab completion)
> lcd ~/temp                              Change local directory (with tab completion)
> put ubuntu-8.04-alternate-i386.iso
> get ubuntu-8.04-desktop-i386.iso
> exit

lftp -c 'open host.com && cd contributed/ubuntu/8.04 && ls'
                                          Execute the given sequence of commands, only if each command succeeds
